cd /path/to/my/project
curl -s http://getcomposer.org/installer | php

Next you need to make a composer.json in the application/ directory of your project (not the application folder) contenant :
--------
{
    "require": {
        
    }
}
-------

composer install

Dans le fichier application/config/config.php de Codeigniter, mettre config['composer_autoload'] = TRUE
